title.narrative: Improved use of gender statistics by different players to inform advocacy, research, policies and programmes

description.narrative: The objective of this SN Outcome is to make gender statistics increasingly accessible and to promote their use by governments, civil society, academia and the private sector to inform research, advocacy, policies and programmes and to promote accountability
